<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>ACLU Store: Rights of. . . Handbooks</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="ffffff">
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><IMG SRC="/graphics/storehdr.gif"></P>
<H1 ALIGN="CENTER">ACLU <I>Rights of. . .</I> Handbooks</H1>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><IMG SRC="/graphics/rbline.gif" WIDTH="80%"></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H4>This series of handbooks is designed to assist individuals with information
about their legal rights in a wide variety of situations.</H4></BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H3>New Titles:</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#1211">The Rights of People with Mental Disabilities</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1213">The Rights of People Who Are HIV Positive</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1212">The Rights of Families</A></LI></UL>
<H3>Topics Covered:</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#1010">Aliens and Refugees</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1020">Authors, Artists, and Other Creative People</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1040">Crime Victims</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1060">Employees and Union Members</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1075">Indians and Tribes</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1077">Lesbians and Gay Men</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1080">Older Persons</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1100">Patients</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1110">Prisoners</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1122">Public Employees</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1125">Racial Minorities</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1140">Students</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1171">Women</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1190">Right to Government Information</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1210">Right to Religious Liberty</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1120">Right to Protest</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="#1200">Right to Privacy</A></LI></UL>
<HR>
<P><A NAME="1010"></A><I><B>The Rights of Aliens and Refugees:</B> <BR>The
Basic ACLU Guide to Alien and Refugee Rights <BR>by David Carliner, Lucas
Guttentag, Arthur C. Helton, and Wade J. Henderson (2nd Edition, 1990)</I></P>
<TABLE BORDER="0" ALIGN="CENTER">
<TR>
<TD><B>Item #1010</B></TD>
<TD WIDTH="40"><BR></TD>
<TD><A HREF="/cgi-bin/aclu/store/as.pl?AddItem=1010&session=970213061654_94&page=handbook.html&lastpage=">Order Item</A></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><B> $8.95</B> + shipping </TD>
<TD></TD>
<TD><A HREF="/cgi-bin/aclu/store/as.pl?View=1&session=970213061654_94&page=handbook.html&lastpage=">View Order</A></TD></TR></TABLE>
<HR>
<P><A NAME="1020"></A>
<I><B>The Rights of Authors, Artists, and Other Creative People:</B> <BR>The
Basic ACLU Guide to Author and Artist Rights<BR>by Kenneth P. Norwick and Jerry
Simon Chasen (2nd Edition, 1992)</I></P>
<TABLE BORDER="0" ALIGN="CENTER">
<TR>
<TD><B>Item #1020</B></TD>
<TD WIDTH="40"><BR></TD>
<TD><A HREF="/cgi-bin/aclu/store/as.pl?AddItem=1020&session=970213061654_94&page=handbook.html&lastpage=">Order Item</A></TD></TR>
