</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#3300CC" VLINK="#003B32" ALINK="#FFFFFF" background = /gif/ermbg12.gif>
<img hspace=20 lowsrc="/gif/library_low.gif" src="/jpeg/library.jpg" WIDTH=500 HEIGHT=167 ALT="Environmental Library"><p>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<B><FONT SIZE=+1>ERM provides current information about the issues that affect you.</B></FONT>
<P>
<b><A HREF="resources">Resources</A></b> - ERM's award-winning publication provides articles on the latest environmental health and safety issues from some of today's industry leaders.  <A HREF="/fyi/resources.html">Register</A> for a complimentary copy.
<p>
<a href="plant/"><b>Plant Exec</b></a> - This newsletter provides articles and topics on facility operations from the plant perspective.  Important regulatory issues and technology trends are covered.  <A HREF="/fyi/plantexec.html">Register</a> for your complimentary copy of Plant Exec.
<P>
<b><A HREF="publications">Publications</A></b> - Informative ERM literature for the EH&amp;S professional including capabilities <A HREF="/library/publications/brochure.html">brochures</A>, cutting-edge <A HREF="/library/publications/article.html">articles</A> by ERM's program specialists, comprehensive <a HREF="/library/publications/lit.html">technical papers</A> and a variety of management, technology and environmental text <A HREF="/global/publications/books.html">books</A> to keep you up-to-date.
<P>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<P>
<CENTER>
