<TITLE>ERM Employment Opportunities</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Martin Schamis,  2-Aug-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#3300CC" VLINK="#003B32" ALINK="#FFFFFF">

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=6 CELLPADDING=6>
<TR><TD VALIGN=top WIDTH=250>
<h2>Employment Opportunities</h2>
<IMG SRC="/gif/employ.gif">
</TD>
<TD ROWSPAN=2>
<P>
The environment affects us all.  Over the last 20 years, protection of the environment and the quest for sustainable development have been growing priorities worldwide.  ERM has developed to meet the needs of business and government in addressing these global challenges.  When you join ERM, you play a major role in this important work.  Few careers can be as rewarding...few employers are as appreciative of talented, dedicated professionals.  ERM's philosophy embraces excellence, diversity, creativity, quality, efficiency and service.  We offer vast opportunities for employment careers.  Select your local region to find out what employment positions are available.

</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=250>

</TD>
</TABLE>
