    <TITLE>Plant Exec - An Update for Plant Environmental Executives</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Martin Schamis, 31-Jul-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="/gif/ermbg5.gif">
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="/gif/exechead.gif" WIDTH="480" HEIGHT="104" ALIGN=bottom>

                <BR>
                <BR><B><FONT SIZE=3>Published by The Environmental Resources Management Group</FONT SIZE></B>
                
        <BR>
        
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING="4">
<TR>
                <TD WIDTH=3></TD>
                <TD VALIGN=TOP><IMG SRC="/gif/ebrochure.gif" ></TD>
                <TD NOWRAP ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP>
                For those environmental professionals who are desperate to <BR>
                hear some good news - you'll want to receive a <a href="/fyi/plantexec.html">free subscription</a><BR> to <b>Plant Exec</b>.
                This newsletter covers ground breaking stories of <BR>environmental compliance success. Each issue highlights a project <BR>in which ERM has helped a client overcome obstacles, save money <BR>and meet environmental, health and safety compliance.  <b>Plant Exec</b> <BR>is where you can read about these stories of compliance success.
<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="/gif/button.gif" HSPACE="15" ALIGN=MIDDLE>
