<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>ERM Seminars</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Martin Schamis, 23-Aug-1996 -->
<!-- Changed by: Jennifer Horn, 30-Sep-1996 -->
<!-- Changed by: Martin Schamis,  8-Nov-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#3300CC" VLINK="#003B32" ALINK="#FFFFFF">

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=6 CELLPADDING=6>
<TR><TD VALIGN=top WIDTH=250>
<h2>Seminars</h2>

</TD>
<TD ROWSPAN=2>
<P>
From the Clean Air Act to ISO 14000, ERM provides a multitude of free seminars every month.  ERM has become renowned for the diversity and quality of our seminar program.  The complimentary presentations are designed to give industry, environmental and legal professionals an overview on up-to-date compliance issues, state-of-the-art management systems and cutting-edge technology.  Check the listing below to find the next ERM seminar nearest you.
<P>
</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=250>
<IMG SRC="/gif/seminar.gif">
</TD>
</TABLE>
<P>

<BR>
<CENTER>
<a href="sem_us.html">U.S. seminars</a> |
<a href="sem_intl.html">international seminars</a> |
<a href="sem_co.html">co-sponsor seminars</a>
</CENTER>

<p>
<center>
<a href="/map/buttonbar.map">
<IMG SRC="/gif/button_bar.gif" WIDTH=484 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 ISMAP USEMAP="#buttonbar"></a>
</center>
<br>



<MAP NAME="buttonbar">
<AREA SHAPE=rect COORDS="0,0,81,34" HREF="/">
<AREA SHAPE=rect COORDS="81,0,162,34" HREF="/comment/">
<AREA SHAPE=rect COORDS="162,0,243,34" HREF="/search/iaquery/">
<AREA SHAPE=rect COORDS="243,0,324,34" HREF="/library/">
<AREA SHAPE=rect COORDS="324,0,402,34" HREF="/newsfront/">
