<HEAD>
<TITLE>ERM Services</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Jamie O'Keefe,  9-Jul-1996 -->
<!-- Changed by: Martin Schamis,  5-Aug-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#3300CC" VLINK="#003B32" ALINK="#FFFFFF">

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=6 CELLPADDING=6>
<TR><TD ALIGN=top WIDTH=250>
<IMG SRC=/gif/services_head.gif>
</TD>
<TD ROWSPAN=2>
<P>
Since its inception in 1977, Environmental Resources Management (ERM) has become a major player in the global environmental marketplace. Our worldwide network of resources has enabled us to provide sound environmental solutions to clients in more than 160 countries for almost every industry sector from chemical manufacturing to transport engineering. Search the information below to discover how ERM's global partnership uses a unique integration of scientific, economic and management services to overcome environmental challenges in both the developed and developing countries.
</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=250>

</TD>
</TABLE>
