<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H3>

<!-- heading -->
ERM IS UK'S TOP ENVIRONMENTAL CONSULTING FIRM 
</H3>

<!-- text -->
EXTON, Pa. -- July  9, 1996 -- Environmental Resources Management (ERM) Group is the United Kingdom's top multiservice environmental consulting firm, according to an independent market survey carried out by Environmental Data Services.  The survey, <I>Environmental Consultancy in the UK:  A Market Analysis 1995</I>, highlights ERM as the only company making the top 20 in each of 12 work areas, a cross-section that includes the treatment of contaminated land, environmental management and auditing, and waste management.  The survey estimates that during the past two years the sector has grown by about 25 percent to an annual turnover of more than $600-million. 
<p>	ERM is also singled out as the most globally active among the nearly 400 environmental consulting firms operating in the U.K.  "We had to get global to maintain our position," says Robin Bidwell, CEO of ERM in the U.K.  "Clients were looking for offices near where they operated and since the late 1980s, we have located offices across Europe and Asia and are developing a presence in South America."  
<p>	The survey points to a maturing market in which growth in spending has slowed since the rapid expansion of the late 1980s.  "Still, growth could double its turnover by 2000 -- if businesses take up environmental management systems, legislation is properly enforced and new legislative drivers are introduced," Bidwell remarks.  


</BLOCKQUOTE>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
<H6>
ERM Group is a global consulting organization of 2,400 environmental, health and safety specialists at more than 90 locations in 24 countries.  The firm is one of the world's largest providers of environmental consulting and engineering services to industry, and offers air quality, wastewater, hazardous and solid waste management; site assessment and remediation; human health and ecological risk assessment; process safety; management consulting; information management; analytical laboratory services and turnkey construction.
</H6>
