<TITLE>Co-sponsor Seminars</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Martin Schamis,  8-Nov-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#3300CC" VLINK="#003B32" ALINK="#FFFFFF">


<h2>Co-sponsor Seminars</h2>

<P>


<b>New Source Review</b> - This workshop will present the fundamental requirements of the new source review (NSR) program under Title I of the Clean Air Act.  The presentation will provide information on the NSR regulations, as interpreted by policy memos.  The changes proposed as a result of the 1990 Clean Air Act Amendments will also be incorporated into each presentation topic.  Finally, the status of the NSR Reform effort, and its potential effects on the current regulations, will be discussed.
<p>
<center>
<TABLE WIDTH=400 BORDER=0>
<TR><TD>
