3/6/976-3/7/97</TD><TD>
Kenneth Weiss
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>
<p>
<b>Negotiating a Title V Permit</b> - This workshop is designed for industry staff and officials who have the responsibility for developing the permit applications for their facility.  
