<p>
<li><B>Information Management:</B>  work group solutions, technical data management, geographical information systems, customized software development, system integration, CAD services, hands-on client training

<p>
<li><B>Construction Management:</B>  facility design/build, facility construction management, facility ownership/operation/maintenance, water collection, conveyance and treatment systems, landfill and lagoon closure, decontamination/demolition, underground and aboveground storage tanks, air emissions control systems, asbestos abatement, lead abatement

<p>
<li><B> Engineering:</B>  design services, siting and permitting, chemical process engineering, system expansions, facility construction/operation/maintenance, stormwater management, geotechnical services, thermal treatment processes

<p>
<li><B> Air Quality Management:</B>  emission inventory plans, analytical services, atmospheric dispersion and deposition modeling, exposure assessments, control technology evaluations, Title V permitting, state permitting, state and federal regulatory assessments, accidental release programs, new source review

<p>
