</td><td><h5>Managing compliance with air pollution regulations, 
particularly the Title V/ Part '70 Operating Permit Program, is 
now more challenging and information- intensive than ever.  
A*I*M*S-Title V is a software tool developed by ERM to assist 
facilities with Title V compliance and is based on our nationwide 
Title V permitting and air compliance management experience. 
<P>
An un-compiled Microsoft Access&#174; 2.0 relational database, 
A*I*M*S-Title V stresses flexibility and openness; connectivity 
with existing electronic data; rapid customization to individual 
State Title V programs; and management of ongoing compliance needs.  
We invite you to explore our site to see our unique approach and to 
preview our system.  Please contact us via 
