<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Yo! Girls
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="../images/yogirl.gif">
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>Welcome to the Town Square of WomenSpace -- the place where you voice your own opinions about lots of different topics.  Breeze through the info below and let your voice be heard!


<BR><BR></FONT>
<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center><BR>
<IMG SRC="../images/ygtool.gif" BORDER=0></a>You could be featured in an upcoming "Girl Power" book for and about young women and girls.  The author is looking for lots of young women to share their opinions about growing up -- <a href="hcordes.html">just click here to find out more ...</a><BR><BR>
<IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center>
<IMG SRC="../images/ygtool.gif" BORDER=0></a>Should your gynecologist be in <a href="../../twp/directory.html">The Women's Pharmacy Directory of Women's Health Care Professionals</a>?  She (he) should be if you consider them to be excellent providers of the best in women's health care.  If you'd like to nominate your women's health care provider to be on our list, <a href="mailto:ADOrmond@aol.com">email us</a> to let us know more about them.

<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center>
<IMG SRC="../images/ygtool.gif" BORDER=0></a>
Ever had a guy swivel his head in some gorgeous woman's direction, then coolly turn to you and say, "Wanna come home with me and get buck naked?" Yup, we're talking about BAD DATES!  And we mean the worst of the worst! <a  href="mailto:adormond@aol.com">Click here to send us yours</a> -- to be included in an upcoming issue of WomenSpace.  But beware -- if they're not bad enough, we just might have to include some of our own!<BR><BR>
<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center>
<IMG SRC="../images/ygtool.gif" BORDER=0></a>
We'll be dedicating an upcoming issue to pregnancy and reproductive health, entitled "My body, My baby." We're looking for submissions from women who have been or thought they were pregnant, who have had or considered having an abortion, or who have had to personally deal with other reproductive issues such as miscarriage, ectopic pregnancies, natural childbirth, or adoption.  Please e-mail Kym at <a href="mailto:adormond@aol.com">adormond@aol.com</a> if you'd be interested in sharing your story; all submissions will be kept confidential.<BR><BR>
<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center><BR>
<p>Do you want to be published? We're having an open call for submissions -- from articles and personal stories to photos, poems, and graphic designs! <a  href="mailto:adormond@aol.com"> E-mail Kym</a> with your ideas!</p><center>
<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center><BR>

