<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: The Women's Pharmacy
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#3E8C29" VLINK="407330">

<TABLE BORDER=0>
<TD WIDTH=100 ALIGN="center" VALIGN="top">

<IMG SRC="logosml.gif">
<BR><BR>
<IMG HEIGHT="340" WIDTH="1" SRC="line.gif">
</TD>
<TD WIDTH=350 ALIGN="center" VALIGN="top">

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR><BR><BR><BR>

<A NAME="1">
<strong> What is The Women's Pharmacy?</strong></center><BR>
The Women's Pharmacy is a mail order pharmacy service fulfilling women's prescription
and over-the-counter product needs.  By working in partnership with RxAmerica, a
licensed mail order pharmacy, we can provide women of all ages a new way to purchase
pharmaceutical products -- and we can save you both money and time!<P><HR><BR>


<strong> <center> Why was The Women's Pharmacy created?</strong> </center><BR>
How many times have you made that dreaded trip to the drug store to purchase some
personal product like tampons, birth control, a pregnancy test -- only to run into a
friend, a co-worker or, worse, a drug store clerk who screams for a PRICE CHECK for the
condoms you're buying?  <P>
It has always seemed rather strange to us that the items that are the most personal are
sold in the most public of places.  This is why we created The Women's <br>Pharmacy --
to provide the much needed privacy and convenience in shopping for personal
products.<P><HR><BR>

<strong><center>What Can I Purchase from <br>The Women's
Pharmacy?</strong></center><BR>
Our product list includes both branded and generic prescription and over-the-counter
women's products.  Because we work with RxAmerica, a full-service, licensed mail order
pharmacy, we can fulfill virtually pharmaceutical need for women and their families. 
Take a look at our over-the-counter <a href="prodlst.html"><B>Product
List.</B></a><P>

</FONT>
</TABLE>
<center><a href="about2.html"><img src="more2.gif" BORDER=0></a></center>
