http://www.womenspace.com:80/spring/gettingpersonal/03camp.html 199.224.6.50 19970208232722 text/html 8516
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 08 Feb 1997 23:23:48 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Set-Cookie: Apache=widener1029485544422881; path=/
Content-length: 8293
Last-modified: Wed, 07 Aug 1996 19:30:52 GMT
