<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Embarassing Tales
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="../images/bodyshock.gif" BORDER=0>
<P>When we asked about your most totally embarrassing moments -- you revealed to us stories that were funny, outrageous and amazingly similar!  It just goes to show that we're all in this thing together! </P>

<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center><BR>

<P>
Last year in 6th grade we had a jeans day.  (When you bring in 50 cans and get to wear jeans.)  In math class I asked my teacher if I could go to the bathroom.  She said yes and I went.  While in the bathroom I took down my bun.  Which made me look like Tina Turner!  Naturally I thought everyone was going to laugh at THAT.  Well I walked in and they did laugh.  But not at THAT.  My teacher came to me and in her southren accent she said "Megan, your fly is opened!"  While in front of me I carefully zipped up my jeans!! </P>
<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center><BR>

<P>
When I was 12, I was on the girls' local swim team.  My mom is normally pretty cool, but can be a bit strict, I guess you could say.  Anyway, one day we were out shopping and I was bugging her for a new swimsuit that I could wear at the swim meet we had coming up later that day.  When I told her which one I wanted, she wouldn't let me have it because she said it was too revealing.  I should have known better than to push the issue but I wanted that suit.  I begged and begged but she still said no. </P>

<P>She gave me enough money to buy another suit that made me look ridiculous so I bought the one I wanted instead.   When I came downstairs in the new suit, she threw a fit that I had gotten the wrong suit.  Then she wanted me to  wear a robe since there wasn't enough time to put a different suit on.  I wouldn't do that either, because I looked silly in a robe.  None of the other girls wore them, so I wasn't going to either. </P>

<P>So, mom said that too much of my butt hung out and she wasn't going to be seen with HER daughter looking like that.  I  fussed and fussed and she totally blew up.  She grabbed me by the arm and hustled me upstairs -- I thought that she was going to make me change, but instead she hauled me to her room where she pulled out her makeup stool sat down and drug me over her lap.  She gave me the hardest spanking, then took me to the swim meet where all the other girls could see that it was plainly obvious that I had just gotten a spanking -- from the hand prints that stuck out of the sides of the suit that didn't cover much to  begin with.  The girls teased me so bad I coudn't compete.</P>

<P>For the rest of the year, they teased me about getting spanked.  Let that be a lesson girls ... Do as mom says... !!!!</P>

<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center><BR>
<P>
Well, in my last period class one day, it seemed like everyone was looking at me and telling secrets.  So I asked  someone what was up, and they said, "nothing". I had just started my period that week, but I decided that I'd wait until I got home to change my pad. </P>

<P>So when the class was over, I walked to my locker and asked my friend what everyone was talking about.  She said she didn't know.  But she kept trying to walk behind me.  So when I was out waiting for my bus a deaf girl from class spelled out "blood" in sign language.  I just about died.  I  went home and found blood all over the back of my jeans. </P>

<P>I called my mom at work in tears.  She said, "it's going to happen to someone and that someone is  you.  Don't worry about it; every girl goes through this at some time or another."  To this day, when I have my period I try to change my pad as often as possible.  I am so self-conscious now.  Oh and that so-called friend that acted like she didn't know what was going on; she's not my friend any longer. </P>

<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center><BR>
<P>
When I was skiing in Colorado, I was about to get off the lift of the bunny slope when my jacket got caught and I couldn't get off. By the time I got my jacket loose, I had reached the top of a black diamond slope.  Since it was my first time skiing, I just freaked out totally. </P>

<P>I decided to sit on my butt and slide down the steep slope.  I was proud of myself when I'd almost reached the bottom, but was embarassed to see my friend's cute brother applauding me.  A bunch of people were laughing at me, and I realized when I looked behind me that I had started my period.  I had left a trail behind me!  I was so horrified and refused to go out again for the rest of the week!</P>
<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif" BORDER=0></center><BR>


