<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Angel Power
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="../images/bodyshock.gif">
<FONT SIZE=+1><P><center>Angel, our heroine of puberty, knows very well that growing up can be tough at times.  She relies on her pal, Bell, to see her through the roughest parts of life  -- like starting your period, dealing with your friends, figuring out guys, body changes ... all the things that happen during BodyShock!</center></P>

</FONT><BR>
<center><img src="../images/rulepk.gif">
<BR><BR>
<P><B>Hey Girls, Angel here ... with my pal, Bell</b></P>

<P>Ya say you just can't deal with one more crazy BodyShock change?  One day ... acne, the next day ... body hair, the following day ... you start your period.  I can totally relate -- and, believe me, it's not so easy to deal with!</P>
<P> But the important thing that you HAVE to remember is:</P>

<center><H1>You Have The Power To Handle It!</H1></center>
<center><img src="../images/angelpower.gif"></center>


<P>In no time at all you'll soar right through these crazy days.  Just grab a friend and have fun along the way!</P></center>

<center><img src="../images/rulepk.gif"></center><BR>
<center>
<a href="../index.html"><IMG SRC="../images/wstool.gif" BORDER=0></a><BR>
<a href="../gettingpersonal/personal.html"><IMG SRC="../images/gptool.gif" BORDER=0></a>
<a href="bodyshock.html"><IMG SRC="../images/bstool.gif" BORDER=0></a>
<a href="../yogirls/yogirls.html"><IMG SRC="../images/ygtool.gif" BORDER=0></a>
