<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Opinions Needed
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<center><IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="../images/yogirl.gif"></center>
<FONT SIZE=+1> <BR>You could be featured in an upcoming "Girl Power" book!  Find out how below ...<BR><BR><BR> 

<BR><center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif"></center><BR>

<P>Hi, my name is Helen Cordes and I'd like to interview you for a book I'm writing on girls and body image. Read the info below and if you'd like to be interviewed by email, just <a href="mailto:hcordes@igc.apc.org">click here</a> to let me know!  </FONT></P>
<BR><center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif"></center>

<BR>The book will be written FOR girls aged 9-14 (or older, or younger -- whoever wants to read it!), and it's part of the "Girl Power" series from Lerner Publications in Minneapolis.  The real experts in this book are going to be girls, so I'm looking for lots of girls to tell me about their experiences and give me advice for other girls.</P>
<P>Here's what I'm going to cover in the book:</P>
<UL>
<LI>The pressure girls feel to be "pretty" and thin.<BR>
I'd like to know how you feel about how you look, and what you do to keep yourself from going crazy about your looks.<BR><BR>
<LI>Ways girls feel self-confident about their body.<BR>
Do you feel self-confident about your body (and your brain's) abilities?<BR><BR>
<LI>Ways girls feel good about how their body is changing in the teen years.<BR>
Lots of things changing below the neck, and above (ZITS!) -- how are you handling it?<BR>
</UL>
<P>That's the basics -- and I'd love to hear from you!  So if you'd like to participate, <a href="questions.html">click here</a> to read a list of questions I'd like you to think about.  You can either <a href="mailto:hcordes@igc.apc.org">email me directly</a> with your thoughts on the topics above OR, even better, <a href="mailto:hcordes@igc.apc.org">click here</a> to request to have these questions emailed to you.</P>

<center><IMG SRC="../images/rulepk.gif"></center><BR><BR>
<center>
<a href="../index.html"><IMG SRC="../images/wstool.gif" BORDER=0></a><BR>
<a href="../gettingpersonal/personal.html"><IMG SRC="../images/gptool.gif" BORDER=0></a>
