<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace:Fall '95
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFA55">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="daisystem2.gif">
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>
Welcome to the first Space on the Web dedicated to young women and girls!!  If you've been searching the Web for a cool place to hang out and talk about things like the changes occurring in your body, growing up, relationships, sexuality, your health -- you've come to the right Space!</P>
<P>

In WomenSpace, you can feel totally comfortable exploring all the issues that are important to young women and girls.  We'll cover lots of territory  -- from starting your period and buying bras to choosing a method of birth control, avoiding sexually transmitted diseases, working on your relationships and exploring sexuality.  </FONT>
</P>  
<P>Within WomenSpace, you can also find out about all kinds of women's personal products -- and you can even learn about new ways to purchase them through <a href="../twp/pharmacy.html"><B>The Women's Pharmacy</b></a>.</P>

<P>Take a look at all the different areas within this first issue of WomenSpace ... and let us know what you think!<P>
<HR>
<P>
<a href="personal.html"><img align=left src="daisyl.gif" BORDER=0></a>If you have concerns about health, sexuality, relationships or birth control, check out all the great features in <B><a href="personal.html">Getting Personal</a></B> -- like our cool interactive <a href="bc.html"><B>Birth Control Questionnaire</b></a>, the <a href="std.html"><B>STD Guide</b></a> -- and a special feature on taking care of your <a href="osteo.html"><b>bones</b></a>.  Get the inside scoop on the best tips for <a href="shaving.html"><B>shaving</B></a> -- our picks for the <a href="top.html"><B>Top 10</B></a> worst reasons to decide to have sex for the first time -- and get acquainted with <a href="missconceptions.html"><B>Miss Conceptions</B></a> -- our very poorly informed know-it-all!  <P>
<HR><P>
<a href="bodshk.html"><img align=left src="daisyo.gif" BORDER=0></a>We have an awesome area just for <em>girls</em> where you can find information about all the changes occurring in your body.  In our first issue of <a href="bodshk.html"><B>Bodyshock</B></a>, we get into the nitty-gritty of <a href="shaving.html"><B>shaving</B></a> -- just about everything you need to know on the topic!   We also have a special story feature about <a href="pimple.html"><B>pimples</B></a> and, most importantly, you've just gotta meet our new heroine of puberty -- <a href="angel.html"><b>Angel</b></a>.<P>
<P><HR><BR>
<a href="girls.html"><img align=left src="daisyp.gif" BORDER=0></a>Hey, WomenSpace isn't a place just for us to speak -- <a href="mailto:ADOrmond@aol.com"><B>we want to hear from you!</B></a>  Check out <a href="girls.html"><b>Yo! Girls</b></a> where we've listed the "topics of the day" -- whether you have a story to tell, a thought to share or a point to make, we want it know about it!  <BR><BR><BR><BR>
<P><HR><BR><BR>
<a href="shop.html"><img align=left src="daisybl.gif" BORDER=0></a>With all the new products that come out every day for young women, how's a girl to keep up with what's what? Check out <B><a href="shop.html">The Grrl Store</a></B> where you can preview all the latest and greatest in health products.  In this issue, you'll get a run down on the best shaving accessories in <a href="thiarating.html"><b>Thia's Thoughts On ... </b></a> soap, foam or gel??</P><BR><BR>
<P>
<HR>
WomenSpace is sponsored by <B><a href="../twp/pharmacy.html">The Women's Pharmacy</a></B> -- the first mail order pharmacy for women's prescription and over-the-counter personal products.  Now, getting refills on your birth control pills is as easy as opening your mail box ...

<P>
And remember, we frequently update WomenSpace with
new information -- so visit us often to keep up on hot 
info about young women's health.
