<center>You've just entered WomenSpace -- a grrlfriend-ly place in CyberSpace for young women and girls to hangout!  Welcome and thanks for all your emails of encouragement and support for WomenSpace.  As you cruise through all the articles, stories and info inside, don't forget that WomenSpace is UpDaTeD from time to time with all new features.  To keep up on what's new, sign up below to receive the WomenSpace UpDaTe. </center>
</P></FONT>
