<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: The Women's Pharmacy
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#3E8C29" VLINK="407330">

<TABLE BORDER=0>
<TD WIDTH=100 ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN="top">

<IMG SRC="logosml.gif">
<BR><BR>
<IMG HEIGHT="540" WIDTH="1" SRC="line.gif">
</TD>
<TD WIDTH=350 ALIGN="center" VALIGN="top">

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR><BR><BR><BR><strong><center>Do I have to join an insurance plan to use <br>The Women's
Pharmacy?</strong></center><P>
</CENTER>
No!  The Women's Pharmacy is for all women -- regardless of your insurance or managed
care plan.  In fact, we designed the plan primarily for the benefit of those women who
do not have prescription coverage -- as well as for those who's prescription plans do
not cover items like oral contraceptives. <P>
You may use your credit card (MasterCard, Visa, Discover) or mail in your payment for
your products.  If you do have insurance coverage for your prescription products, call
your insurance provider to determine if your plan will accept RxAmerica as a pharmacy.
<P>

<LI>If so, you can call us at 1-800-293-2202 to process your order and assist you in
filing the claim. <br>
<LI>If not, you can still use The Women's Pharmacy -- you'll just need to file the
claim directly with your insurance plan.<P><HR><BR>
<A NAME="5">
<strong> <center>What are the advantages of using <br>The Women's Pharmacy?</strong>
</center><BR>
<LI><strong>Great Prices</strong> -- Our prescription and over-the-counter product
prices are very competitive with retial drug stores.<P>
<LI><strong>Convenient Home Delivery</strong> -- Simply phone or mail in your order and
it will be processed and shipped by First Class Mail or UPS within 48 hours.<P>
<LI><strong>Private Consultations</strong> -- You can always request to speak with a
female pharmacist when you have questions about your products, prescriptions or
health.<P>
<LI><strong>Access To Pharmacists</strong> -- You'll always find the Rx America
pharmacists eager to help you.<P>
<LI><strong>Automatic Refills</strong> -- You can have your refills for such products
as oral contraceptives shipped to you automatically.<P>
<LI><strong>Women's Health Information</strong> -- You'll receive special membership
discounts from the National Women's Health Resource Center which includes their
bi-monthly newsletter on women's health.<P>
<LI><strong>Highly Qualified Pharmacists</strong> -- Your prescriptions will be filled
by registered pharmacists using one of the most technologically advanced pharmacy
systems available.<P>
</B></a><P>

</FONT>
</TABLE>
