<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Angel Power
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="../images/bodyshock.gif">
<FONT SIZE =+1>
<P><CENTER><BR>Order Your Own Copy of <BR>
<B>Ten Rules To Survive BodyShock!</B></center>
<BR>
<BR><BR><BR><center><img src="../images/rulepk.gif"><BR></center>
<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="../../winter/images/angel3.gif" BORDER=0><BR><BR>
</FONT>
<B>Ten Rules to Survive BodyShock!</B> is every girl's guide to dealing with growing up. It's an eighteen page booklet that features Angel and her best friend, Bell, learning about the "rules" of growing up -- and particularly about starting your period.  Angel finds out the truth behind the myths -- gets some advice from Bell -- and learns about all the positive things that go along with experiencing what she calls "BodyShock!"</P>

<P>If you've already experienced growing up for yourself, then <B>Ten Rules to Survive BodyShock!</B> is a perfect gift to give to any young woman or girl in your life.  Growing up is hard enough for girls these days ... why not give them something positive to read and some fun along the way?</P><HR>
