<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Birth Control Questionnaire
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="DEA7D4">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="daisystem2.gif">
<FONT SIZE =+1>
<P>Exploring birth control options ... <BR><BR><BR>
In the Getting Personal area of WomenSpace, we believe in sharing information with young women to help them make important decisions -- such as whether or not to become sexually active.   Although we feel that <b>abstinence</b> is both a valid and very mature choice for young women to make -- we also realize that, today, young women need a great deal more information in order to make the best decision for themselves.  
<P>
If you've reached a point in your life -- or in your relationship  -- in which you feel you need more information about birth control options, you've probably already discovered that there are lots of things to consider -- your 
lifestyle, your relationship and the costs of the birth control methods are
just a few. 
<P>
The following interactive <strong>Birth Control Questionnaire</strong> is meant to provide you with some things to consider as you explore the contraceptive options that may be best for you.<P></FONT>
<P>
<BR><BR>
<A NAME="you"><HR>
<strong>1. Which of the following best describes you?</strong><BR>
A.  I am a creature of habit -- I have daily routines which I follow
carefully. <a href="bc1a.html">(Answer 1A)</a><BR>
B.  I am pretty good at remembering to do things each day. <a href="bc1b.html">(Answer 1B)</a><BR>
C.  I am sometimes forgetful and often have to be reminded to do things. <a href="bc1c.html">(Answer 1C)</a><BR>
<BR><BR>
<P>
<A NAME="relate"><HR>
<strong>2. Which of the following best describes your current relationship(s)?</strong><BR>
A.  My boyfriend and I have just begun to have sex but, so far, we haven't
discussed birth control. <a href="bc2a.html">(Answer 2A)</a><BR>
B.  I have had (or am having) sex with one or more partners -- but I don't
consider any of them to be "boyfriends" or steady partners.  <a href="bc2b.html">(Answer 2B)</a><BR>
C.  My boyfriend and I will probably be having sex in the near future and
we have begun to discuss birth control options. <a href="bc2c.html">(Answer 2C)</a><BR>
<BR><BR>
<A NAME="buy"><HR>
<strong>3. Who will purchase the birth control method that you and your partner use?</strong><BR>
A.  My partner buys the birth control. <a href="bc3a.html">(Answer 3A)</a><BR>
B.  I buy the birth control.  <a href="bc3b.html">(Answer 3B)</a><BR>
C.  We share the cost of birth control.  <a href="bc3c.html">(Answer 3C)</a><BR><BR><BR>

<HR>
