<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Top Ten
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="DEA7D4">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="daisystem2.gif">
<FONT SIZE =+1>

<P><BR>
Making the decision to become sexually active is a big one. Think it through carefully and make your decision based on what is best for YOU!  Take a look at some <em>not so good</em> reasons to
become sexually active -- and ask yourself if any of these sound familiar...   <P>
<HR>The 10 worst reasons to decide to have sex for the first time -- and
helpful tips on how to avoid making the list!<P>

<P>
<P>
<A NAME="1">
1.  Your boyfriend says he wants to break up with you because you won't
have sex with him.  <a href="avoid1.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<A NAME="2">
2.  All of your girlfriends talk about having sex with their boyfriends and
you feel left out of the conversation. <a href="avoid2.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<A NAME="3">
3.  Your boyfriend begs so often, you decide to do it just to make him
leave you alone. <a href="avoid3.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<A NAME="4">
4.  You hate being called a virgin. <a href="avoid4.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<A NAME="5">
5.  Your boyfriend tells you that his ex-girlfriend and he always had sex
and wants to know "what's your problem?" <a href="avoid5.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<A NAME="6">
6.  Your boyfriend tells you that if you want to prove that you truly love
him, you'll have sex with him. <a href="avoid6.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<A NAME="7">
7.  You meet a new guy to whom you are incredibly attracted but whom you've
just met. <a href="avoid7.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<A NAME="8">
8.  Your friends make fun of you because they've done it and you haven't. <a href="avoid8.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<A NAME="9">
9.  Your boyfriend tells you that all of his friends are teasing him
because you won't give in. <a href="avoid9.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<A NAME="10">
10.  Your parents are so overbearing that you decide to have sex with your
boyfriend to secretly get back at them. <a href="avoid10.html">(Avoid the list!)</a><P>
<P>
<HR>
<P>What is the worst reason you've ever heard?  Tell us in <a href="girls.html"><b>Yo! Girls</b></a>.
</FONT>
<HR>

