<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Miss Conceptions
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="DEA7D4">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="daisystem2.gif">
<FONT SIZE =+1>
<P>
<BR><BR>

<CENTER>
The Truth About
Miss Conceptions ... </CENTER>
<BR><BR><BR><BR>

<P>When I was in high school, I had a girlfriend who seemed to know everything about everything -- guys, dating, kissing, making out -- even about having sex! I'll call her Miss Conceptions for now, to protect her identity. </P> </FONT>

<P>She always seemed so mature, so worldly, so knowledgable, so sure of herself that, quite honestly, I believed her most of the time. Because I didn't have too much experience in either of these areas, I really looked up to her and the so-called advice that she gave me during that time. </P>

<P>There were lots of girls at my school who believed Miss Conceptions. In fact, one time when we had a sleep-over at her house, we stayed up all night listening to her tell stories of the worst things that could happen when you start making out with a guy.</P>

<P>Not until much later did I discover the truth about Miss Conceptions -- and the real facts about all those things that I worried about back then. As it turns out, she was just as CLUELESS as I was back then -- only she covered it up by making up crazy tales.
</P>
<P>Now that I am older and a whole lot wiser, I feel it is my duty as a fellow girl to clear up some of the myths caused by Miss Conceptions. Here are just a few of her famous words -- along with my own words of wisdom! </P>
<BR>
<A NAME="1">
<P><B>Miss Conceptions:</B>	"You can have sex without using any birth control when you have your period because you can't get pregnant then." <a href="wrong.html">(Wrong!)</a> </P>
<A NAME="2">
<P><B>Miss Conceptions:</B>	"You only have to take a birth control pill on the day you
plan to have sex in order for it to work." <a href="c'mon.html">(C'mon!)</a></P>
<A NAME="3">
<P><B>Miss Conceptions:</B>	"If you put on your brother's or your boyfriend's shorts,
you can get pregnant." <a href="noway.html">(No Way!)</a></P>
<A NAME="4">
<P><B>Miss Conceptions:</B>	"If you've been having sex with your boyfriend for a while
without using any birth control, it means that you're sterile." <a href="wrongagain.html">(Wrong again!)</a> </P>
<A NAME="5">
<P><B>Miss Conceptions:</B>	"If you jump up and down after having sex, you won't get
pregnant." <a href="getreal.html">(Get real!)</a></P>
<A NAME="6">
<P><B>Miss Conceptions:</B>	"You can't get pregnant the first time you have sex."
<a href="forgetit.html">(Forget it!)</a></P>
<A NAME="7">
<P><B>Miss Conceptions:</B>	"If I guy pulls out while you're having sex, you won't get
pregnant." <a href="getaclue.html">(Get a clue!)</a></P>
<A NAME="8">
<P><B>Miss Conceptions:</B>	"The first day you start the Pill you can have sex without
worrying about getting pregnant." <a href="wrongo.html">(Wrongo!)</a> </P>
<A NAME="9">
<P><B>Miss Conceptions:</B>	"If you use the bathroom right after having sex, you can
kill the sperm." <a href="wishful.html">(Wishful thinking!)</a></P>
<BR><BR>
If you, too, have Miss Conceptions running aroung your school, clue her in to the real facts!!
