<TITLE>
WomenSpace: BodyShock
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="F7B68B">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="daisystem2.gif">
<FONT SIZE =+1>
<CENTER>Hey, no one ever said puberty was totally pleasant -- but it certainly doesn't have to be the pits either!  </CENTER><P><BR>Especially when you have all the facts. BodyShock is a place just for girls where we talk about all the changes that happen in your body.  We'll have some fun too!! <P> <CENTER>Check out this issue of<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+2>BodyShock</FONT><BR>
-- and let us know what you think! </CENTER><BR>
<P>

<P><HR>
<a href="angel.html"><img align=left src="daisyo.gif" BORDER=0></a><EM>REGULAR FEATURES</EM><BR>
Meet <a href="angel.html"><B>Angel</B></a> -- our heroine of puberty!  She's learning the facts the hard way -- but she's more than willing to share what she knows. With each issue of BodyShock, you can check out Angel's progress -- and you can give her some advice in <a href="girls.html"><b>Yo! Grrls</b></a>.
<P><HR>

<a href="shaving.html"><img align=left src="daisyo.gif" BORDER=0></a><EM>SPECIAL FEATURES</EM><BR>
In this issue, you'll find just about everything you ever wanted to know about <a href="shaving.html"><b>shaving</b></a>.  In fact, we've got the low-down on ... if you should, when you should, how you should and what you should use -- should you decide to!!<P><BR>
<P>
<HR>
<a href="pimple.html"><img align=left src="daisyo.gif" BORDER=0></a><EM>SPECIAL STORY FEATURES</EM><BR>
Read a great story  -- that just might be true -- about a girl who says she had a <a href="pimple.html"><B>"Pimple on My Dimple"</B></a>!  If you've got a story to share in BodyShock -- about growing up, your most totally embarrassing situation, the changes happening in your body --  just let us know in <a href="girls.html"><b>Yo! Girls</b></a>.<BR><BR>
