<HR>
<FONT SIZE =+1>
<P>

Calling all grrls!  <BR>
We want to hear from you ...<BR><BR>
<img src="images/yobig.gif" BORDER=0></CENTER>
<BR><BR><BR>
Boy Oh Boy! (oops, I mean, Girl Oh Girl!) ... we received tons of emails from you after the first issue of WomenSpace!!!  Thanks for the gab ... but, now, we gotta hear what you think about a few other things ... <BR><BR>
<HR>
<img src="images/yosmall.gif" BORDER=0><BR>
Everyday there are millions of young women and girls out there logging on to the Internet!  And we think grrls are pretty close to totally dominating CyberSpace.  Afterall we're already the best at writing, creating, searching, finding, communicating, etc.  We want to hear if you agree.  <a href="mailto:ADOrmond@aol.com">Email us with your reasons for why you think that Girls Rule Online!</a>
<HR>
<img src="images/yosmall.gif" BORDER=0><BR>
WomenSpace wants to know about your roommate horror stories!  Any roommate will do ... from your sister ... to your freshman roommate at college  ... to your first live-in boyfriend (or even husband!).  We're compiling a list of what to look for in a roommate -- and what characteristics to avoid!  So if you've got a specific incident to share or any general comments to make about what makes a good or bad roommate -- we want to hear about them!  <a href="mailto:ADOrmond@aol.com">Click here to email them to us!</a>

