<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Reality
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<center>
<A NAME="7"><IMG SRC="images/wssmall.gif" BORDER=0><BR><HR>
<a href="personal.html">Back to Getting Personal Main Page</a> <BR><a href="index.html">WomenSpace</a> | <a href="bodshk.html">BodyShock</a> | <a href="yogirls.html">Yo! Girls</a> | <a href="grrlstore.html">The Grrl Store</a> | 
<a href="extra.html">Extra! Extra!</a> | <a href="hotlinx.html">Hot Linx</a><BR>
<a href="../twp/pharmacy.html">The Women's Pharmacy</a></center>
<HR>
<FONT SIZE =+1>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="images/pers.gif"><BR><BR>
<P>
What's The Deal With <B>Reality</B> --<BR> The Female Condom?<BR>This seems to be a question on lots of young women's minds these days ...<BR>
...What is it? How does it work? Where can I buy it?  Will I like it? <BR>We've heard all of these from women who've been searching for new options for protection against pregnancy and sexually transmitted diseases.</P>
<P>
Well, we've investigated <b>Reality</b> for you ... take a look below at what we found!</P></FONT>

<a href="reality.html#1">It's Easy To Use!</a> | <a href="reality.html#2">It Feels Great!</a> | <a href="reality.html#3">It Puts You In Control!</a> | <a href="reality.html#4">It's Not What You Think!</a><BR><BR><a href="reality.html#5">Where Can I Buy Reality?</a><BR><BR>
<a href="reality.html#6">Get A Reality Coupon And Test It Out!</a>
</CENTER>
<HR>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+1>
Reality is the latest and the greatest in birth control options -- and is arguably the very first option women have ever to protect themselves against sexually transmitted diseases.  Let's face it, the main drawback of regular, male condoms is the fact that they are just that -- MALE condoms -- i.e., women have to have the willing participation of their partners to successfully and correctly use male condoms every time.  Finally, Reality has set in!  With the female condom the playing field has been leveled:  Women can take complete control of their protection against sexually transmitted diseases.</FONT></P>
<A NAME="1">
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>
It's Easy To Use!<BR></FONT>
Because Reality fits inside the woman's vagina -- as opposed to the outside of the man's penis -- women can take control of protection by inserting Reality ahead of time -- no erection required!  <BR><BR><CENTER><a href="reality2.html">(Click here to find out how it works ...)</a></CENTER>
<A NAME="2"><BR></P>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>
It Feels Great!<BR></FONT>
The best news yet is the fact that Reality female condoms simply feel better to both men and women than do male condoms.  Thus, the old argument women have heard for years ("I don't like to wear condoms because they don't feel natural") could be a thing of the past.  The reason that most people give for why they think Reality feels more natural than regular condoms is the fact that Reality is made of polyurethane  -- which allows body heat to be transferred more readily than latex.
<BR><BR><CENTER><a href="reality2.html#2">(Click here to read what others had to say ...)</a><BR></CENTER>
<A NAME="3"><BR></P>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>
It Puts You In Control!<BR></FONT>
Another advantage of the polyurethane is the fact that it's sturdy, yet very thin and soft -- therefore, it provides protection from even the smallest microbes that cause sexually transmitted diseases, like Hepatitis B and HIV, the virus that causes AIDS.  When used correctly every time, you can feel confident that you're doing a great job of protecting yourself against potential infections. 
<BR><BR><CENTER>
<a href="reality2.html#3">(Click here to find out how it protects you ...)</a><BR>
<A NAME="4"><BR></P></CENTER>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>
It's Not What You Think!<BR></FONT>
When Reality first came out on the market last year, a few people commented that it looked "strange" -- and sometimes even sounded strange when you used it.  But the important thing to keep in mind is the fact that everything new and revolutionary seems strange at first!  Women haven't had a such a great new option in a long, long time -- so naturally, it takes a moment to understand Reality before using it.  It's a good idea to take the time to carefully read the instructions before putting the female condom in place.  Practice inserting it before you take it for a spin with your partner!
<BR>
<A NAME="5"><BR></P>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>
Where Can I Buy Reality?<BR></FONT>
You can find Reality in most all of the same stores you find male condoms.  You can also find them at many public health clinics.  But the easiest way to purchase <B>Reality</B> is through The Women's Pharmacy. <BR><BR>
<CENTER><a href="reality2.html#4">(Click here to find out about ordering Reality <BR>through The Women's Pharmacy ...)</a><BR><BR></P></CENTER>
<A NAME="6"><BR></P>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>
Get A Reality Coupon And Test It Out!<BR></FONT>
Hey, don't take our word for it ... try it out for yourself!  Take a look inside <a href="grrlstore.html">The Grrl Store</a> and find out about how to get a coupon for Reality today!
<BR><BR>
<a href="reality.html#7">Back to Top of Page</a></P>
