<FONT SIZE =+1>
<P><CENTER>
<img src="images/pers.gif" BORDER=0><BR><BR>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>
Pantyhose ...  a subject that might seem pretty benign has got everybody talking!  Just about everybody who wrote to us had a pretty strong opinion about them!  <BR>Take a look below at what you had to say on the subject -- and find out about some of the <a href="hosehealth.html">health benefits AND problems</a> of wearing them.<BR><BR><BR></P></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><H2>Pantyhose -- Luv 'Em or Hate 'Em??</H2><BR>
</CENTER><HR>

<UL>
<img src="images/up.gif" BORDER=0>"Pantyhose are great for covering up panty lines -- with slacks or with skirts."<BR>
<BR>

<img src="images/down.gif" BORDER=0>"The only acceptable reason for wearing pantyhose is to wear them on your head and rob a bank."<BR><BR>
<img src="images/up.gif" BORDER=0>"Stockings look great -- and cover blemishes on your legs..."<BR><BR>
<img src="images/down.gif" BORDER=0>"I think men created pantyhose to oppress women."<BR><BR>
<img src="images/down.gif" BORDER=0>"Pantyhose are right up there with high heels -- society's way of saying 'here, make yourself fit!'"<BR><BR>
<img src="images/down.gif" BORDER=0>"Who decided what color 'NUDE' is, anyway? And besides, if I wanted to be NUDE I wouldn't be wearing pantyhose, now would I?"<BR><BR>

<img src="images/up.gif" BORDER=0>"They're sexy yet conservative! Pantyhose are wonderful!"  <BR><BR>
<img src="images/down.gif" BORDER=0>"Most of the time they are easily ripped, and hard to get down when you are in dire need of going to the restroom."<BR><BR>
<img src="images/down.gif" BORDER=0>"Throw them away girls!!  Say no to the hose  : ) Legs are naturally beautiful."<BR><BR>
<img src="images/up.gif" BORDER=0>"Knee-highs are the greatest thing since sliced bread!"<BR><BR>
<img src="images/down.gif" BORDER=0>"I usually hate to put them on, and they don't always agree with the style of your underwear, which makes them all the more uncomfortable!"<BR><BR>
<img src="images/up.gif" BORDER=0>"Sometimes they can help push back something that has gone astray ..."<BR><BR>
<img src="images/down.gif" BORDER=0>"I *hate* pantyhose.  I often refuse to wear them -- they itch, scratch, run and are a major pain.  I only wonder why women are forced to wear the things."<BR><BR>
<img src="images/up.gif" BORDER=0>Thigh highs are the way to go.  I am six feet tall and I have a thirty four inch inseam.  They are wonderful.<BR><BR>

</FONT><BR><BR></UL>
<HR>
Your quotes say it all -- there are as many opinions on wearing pantyhose as there are grrls out there!  But you may want to consider some of the health benefits and problems of wearing pantyhose before making your decision about whether you love 'em or hate 'em.  Take a closer look at <a href="hosehealth.html">the pros and cons of pantyhose.</a></FONT>
