<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Anorexia and Bulimia
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<A NAME="1">
<center><IMG SRC="images/wssmall.gif" BORDER=0><BR><HR>
<a href="personal.html">Back to Getting Personal Main Page</a> <BR><a href="index.html">WomenSpace</a> | <a href="bodshk.html">BodyShock</a> | <a href="yogirls.html">Yo! Girls</a> | <a href="grrlstore.html">The Grrl Store</a> | 
<a href="extra.html">Extra! Extra!</a> | <a href="hotlinx.html">Hot Linx</a><BR>
<a href="../twp/pharmacy.html">The Women's Pharmacy</a></center>
<HR>
<FONT SIZE =+1>
<CENTER>
<img src="images/pers.gif" BORDER=0><BR><BR>
<P>
It seems you can hardly pick up a women's magazine these days without reading something about two types of devastating eating disorders that overwhelmingly plague young women -- anorexia nervosa and bulimia.  You've no doubt heard of them -- but do you really know the symptoms?  </P>
<P>If you suspect that a friend, a sister -- or even you -- may be suffering from an eating disorder, take the following quick health questionnaire.  </P>
<P>
Read the statements under each of the following five categories below.  If you can answer "yes" to more than two of the statements under each category, it may be time to take a closer look at your own health ... <BR><BR></P></FONT>
</CENTER>
<HR>
<FONT SIZE =+1>Category 1</FONT><BR>
<P><FORM><input type="radio" name="fear" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="fear" value="no">No - I have an intense fear of gaining weight and becoming fat.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="skinny" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="skinny" value="no">No - My friends / family tell me that I'm too skinny but I still feel overweight.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="mirror" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="mirror" value="no">No - When I look into the mirror, I see myself as needing to lose even more -- even though I've already lost a lot.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="perfect" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="perfect" value="no">No - I feel constant pressure from myself and others to strive for perfection in everything I do.<BR><BR></FORM>
<BR>
<CENTER><a href="cat1.html">Click here if you can answer "yes" to two or more of these statements.</a><BR><BR><a href="eatdis.html#1">Back to the Top of the Page</a></CENTER>
<A NAME="2">
<HR>
<FONT SIZE=+1>Category 2</FONT>
<FORM><input type="radio" name="body" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="body" value="no">No - Over the last several months, I've lost at least 25% of my body weight by dieting.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="calories" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="calories" value="no">No - I try to eat less than 800 calories each day in order to continue to lose weight.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="period" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="period" value="no">No - I haven't had my period in at least three months.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="tired" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="tired" value="no">No - I often feel very tired and sometimes dizzy.<BR><BR></FORM><BR>
<CENTER><a href="cat2.html">Click here if you can answer "yes" to two or more of these statements.</a><BR><BR><a href="eatdis.html#1">Back to the Top of the Page</a></CENTER>
<A NAME="3"><HR>
<FONT SIZE=+1>Category 3</FONT>
<FORM><input type="radio" name="hair" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="hair" value="no">No - Lately, I've noticed that I am losing lots of hair -- in my brush and in the shower.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="skin" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="skin" value="no">No - My skin is especially dry -- even cracking in places.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="nails" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="nails" value="no">No - I've noticed that my fingernails are particularly brittle and even turn purplish-blue.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="hands" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="hands" value="no">No - My hands and feet are constantly cold and sometimes turn blue.<BR><BR></FORM>
<CENTER><a href="cat3.html">Click here if you can answer "yes" to two or more of these statements.</a><BR><BR><a href="eatdis.html#1">Back to the Top of the Page</a></CENTER>
<A NAME="4"><HR>
<FONT SIZE=+1>Category 4</FONT>
<FORM><input type="radio" name="diet" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="diet" value="no">No - I diet pretty much everyday -- but occassionally I pig out and eat tons of food.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="throw" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="throw" value="no">No - Whenever I pig out or feel like I've just eaten too much, I throw up to avoid those extra calories.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="control" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="control" value="no">No - Sometimes I feel completely out of control when I eat a big meal -- like I can't stop myself from eating.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="lax" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="lax" value="no">No - Sometimes I use laxatives after eating in order to get rid of extra calories.<BR><BR></FORM>
<CENTER><a href="cat4.html">Click here if you can answer "yes" to two or more of these statements.</a><BR><BR><a href="eatdis.html#1">Back to the Top of the Page</a></CENTER>
<A NAME="5"><HR>
<FONT SIZE=+1>Category 5</FONT>
<FORM><input type="radio" name="enamel" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="enamel" value="no">No - My dentist says the enamel on my teeth has eroded -- and has caused some cavities.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="hoarse" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="hoarse" value="no">No - I've noticed that I'm really hoarse and my throat hurts after throwing up.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="constipate" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="constipate" value="no">No - I am sometimes constipated and have pains in my stomach.<BR><BR>
<input type="radio" name="fear" value="yes">Yes<input type="radio" name="fear" value="no">No - I often feel really dehydrated.<BR><BR></FORM>
<CENTER><a href="cat5.html">Click here if you can answer "yes" to two or more of these statements.</a><BR><BR><a href="eatdis.html#1">Back to the Top of the Page</a></CENTER><HR>
<FONT SIZE=+1>If after reading through this questionnaire you find that you (or someone you know) may be experiencing some of these symptoms -- don't hesitate to speak with a health care provider about them.  Though some of these symptoms are clearly more serious than others, both anorexia and bulimia can lead to lots of serious health problems.  But no one has to suffer from these eating disorders -- there is help!  Take a look at some of the <a href="hotlinx.html">resources available on the internet</a> -- and speak to a health care provider to find out about resources near you.</FONT>
<HR>
