<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace:Tampon Chorus Line
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<center><IMG SRC="images/wssmall.gif" BORDER=0><BR><HR>

<a href="bodshk.html">Back to BodyShock Main Page</a> | <a href="index.html">WomenSpace</a> | <a href="personal.html">Getting Personal</a> | <a href="yogirls.html">Yo! Girls</a> | <a href="grrlstore.html">The Grrl Store</a><BR>
<a href="extra.html">Extra! Extra!</a> | <a href="hotlinx.html">Hot Linx</a><BR>
<a href="../twp/pharmacy.html">The Women's Pharmacy</a></center>
<HR>
<P>
<BR><BR>
<CENTER><img src="images/body.gif" BORDER=0><BR>
<FONT SIZE =+1>
<CENTER><P>Lots of girls say they just aren't into the tampon thang -- <BR>'cause they look a little scary.  <BR><BR>But once you try 'em out, you just might find that they're the coolest thing ever to happen to menstruation! Take a closer look ...<BR><BR><BR>
<P><b>Hey, who says having your period has to be a drag?</b></P>
<IMG SRC="images/chorus.gif" BORDER=0>
<P>You can do all the same fun things you normally do -- <BR>like play sports, ride your bike, run, horseback ride, swim, dance -- <BR><b>there are no limits!</b><BR> <BR>Tampons can really help make sure that you don't worry about a thing! When you're using a tampon, you can wear shorts, bathing suits, running pants, tights <BR>... and never give another thought to whether or not anyone can "see anything."  And the best part ... you probably won't feel anything either!  </P><BR>
<P>So don't limit yourself just 'cause you have your period -- <BR><b>get out there and have some fun!</b></P></CENTER></FONT>

