<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Miss Conceptions
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="DEA7D4">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="daisystem2.gif">


<FONT SIZE=+1><BR><BR>
<CENTER>C'mon!</CENTER>
<BR><BR>
<P>Birth control pills are made up of hormones that essentially "trick" your ovaries into not releasing an egg. Just as it takes your body a whole month to complete its hormonal cycle for menstruation, birth control pills take an entire month to fully control your ovaries. Therefore, you have to take a pill every single day -- at the same time everyday for the pill to be effective.</P></FONT>
<P>
<CENTER><a href="missconceptions.html#2">What Will She Think Of Next!</a></CENTER><P>
<BR><BR>
