<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Miss Conceptions
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="DEA7D4">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="daisystem2.gif">

<FONT SIZE=+1>
<BR><BR>
<CENTER>Get Real!</CENTER>
<BR><BR>
<P>The thinking behind this one stems from the idea that jumping up and down will keep the sperm from swimming through your cervix and from reaching the egg. Although sperm are small, they are stubborn! Chances are, they'll get where they're going regardless of any gymnastics. Besides, you could look pretty ridiculous using this as a method of birth control!!</P></FONT>
<P>
<CENTER><a href="missconceptions.html#5">What Will She Think Of Next!</a><P></CENTER>
