<TITLE>
WomenSpace: Joke du Jour
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<A NAME="1">
<center><IMG SRC="images/wssmall.gif" BORDER=0><BR><HR>
<a href="personal.html">Back to Getting Personal Main Page</a> <BR><a href="index.html">WomenSpace</a> | <a href="bodshk.html">BodyShock</a> | <a href="yogirls.html">Yo! Girls</a> | <a href="grrlstore.html">The Grrl Store</a> | 
<a href="extra.html">Extra! Extra!</a> | <a href="hotlinx.html">Hot Linx</a><BR>
<a href="../twp/pharmacy.html">The Women's Pharmacy</a></center>
<HR>

<CENTER>
<img src="images/pers.gif" BORDER=0><BR><BR>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1>
<BR><BR>Joke du Jour!<BR><BR><BR></CENTER>

<P>Three guys were fishing in the ocean when, suddenly, one of them hooked a mermaid and pulled her into the boat. She begged and pleaded for them to let her go -- and, in exchange, she would grant each of them a wish.</P>

<P>When the first guy asked:  "How do we know you can really grant wishes?"
The mermaid said, "Just make any wish and I'll prove it to you."</P>
<P>The first guy said, "Okay!  I want you to double my IQ!"</P>
<P>With a nod of the mermaid's head, he began to prefectly and eloquently recite endless lines of Shakespeare's poetry and analyze each line with extreme insight.</P>
<P>In amazement, the second guy immediately said, "I want you to triple my IQ!"</P>
The mermaid waved her hand and the second guy began to spout all the mathematical solutions to problems that have been stumping scientists of physics for years.</P>
<P>Seeing all of this, the third guy said, "I want you to quintuple my IQ!"</P>
But the mermaid said, "Look, I don't normally try to dissuade anyone from their wishes, but I really think you should reconsider that one."</P>
<P>"No, I definitely want you to quintuple my IQ!" insisted the third guy.</P>
"But it will change your entire view of the universe, it will force you to see things in an entirely different way!  Won't you ask for something else?  A million dollars, anything!?!" pleaded the mermaid.</P>
<P> But no matter what the mermaid said, the guy insisted on having his I.Q. increased by five times its usual power. </P>
<P>So the mermaid sighed and said "Done."</P>
<P>And he became a woman.</P></FONT>
