Order Affirmed in Love (GOAL)</A></DT>

<DD>More Christian Identity material. &quot;Christianity has historically
been a religion of the white race regardless of how hard whites have tried
to convert the world.&quot;</DD>

<DT><IMG SRC="images/ball-blue.gif" HSPACE=7 HEIGHT=14 WIDTH=14 ALIGN=TOP><A HREF="http://www.webcom.com/%7Eezundel/english/welcome.html" TARGET="_top">Z&uuml;ndelsite</A></DT>

<DD>Revisionist literature from Canada's Ernst Z&uuml;ndel. This site was
moved from its original location after Deltanet decided to capitulate to
