with the line 'subscribe Stormwatch' in the message body.</DD>

<DT><IMG SRC="images/ball-blue.gif" HSPACE=7 HEIGHT=14 WIDTH=14 ALIGN=TOP><A NAME="Stormfront-L"></A><B>Stormfront-L</B></DT>

<DD>This is a moderated discussion forum for White Nationalists. It is
currently distributed only in digest format; all messages, which can sometimes
number 20 or 30 a day, are combined into one daily digest. To subscribe,
send e-mail to <A HREF="mailto:listserv@stormfront.org">listserv@stormfront.org</A>
with the line 'subscribe Stormfront-L' in the message body.</DD>

<P>Please note that lists of subscribers are not available through the
&quot;review&quot; or &quot;who&quot; commands to Listserv or any other
means.</P>
