<center><H1>Letters from the Front</H1></center>
<center><IMG  Align=Top SRC="images/barus.gif"></center>

<p>I have now placed all letters in this section and most of those in the archived section
in reverse chronological order. Messages sent here before October can 
be found in the <a href="letters2.htm">archives</a>. Because of the high volume, I am 
reorganizing the archives, with letters archived by month. If you can't find everything right now, 
check back in a day or so.

<p><a href="lform.htm">Write</a> a letter for publication on this page.
Messages with meaningful content  and of reasonable length will be posted 
here eventually. I'm going to try to be good and update this section every 
weekday morning. Some letters will also be included in an upcoming printed edition of
<strong>Stormfront</strong> magazine.

<hr size=4>

<br>  


<hr>    

<h3><i>Keep up the great work, Don, we will triumph.</i></h3>

<p><tt>Fri Oct 20 13:12 EDT 1995</tt>

<p>I am a very proud White Aryan who visits this site and others like it very often. I'm gald that there is a growing number of people concerned with the fate of our race. I encourage all to recruit more concerned Ayrans to further our cause, as I am doing in South Carolina and surrounding areas.

<p><b>A proud white Aryan</b>
<br>South Carolina
<br><a href="mailto: "></a>

<hr>    

