etc.  I am also a proud member of Sons of the Confederacy and Florida Pioneers.
The other half of my family (my mother's side) are Jewish immigrants from Russia.
I am Jewish.  I was Bar Mitzvah'd.  I am marrying a Jewish girl in less than three
weeks.  She feels the same way I do about most issues.

