forget this atrocity! Question: Are you also tired of  Shindlers List 
by chance?

<p>About the STATISTICS that Mr. Truth wrote about. Understand that 
statistics add up to numbers on paper and has very little to do with 
reality! For instance, you mentioned The Bell Curve which illustrates 
the competence and intelligence of certain races from what I gather. 
If I was to believe this garbage, how would one explain how Africans 
built Pyramids in Africa-Egypt and also how would one explain the 
numerous accomplishments of Africans here in America? You see, statistics 
are numbers and those numbers do not account for the many others 
outside of that perimeter.  Sure, alot of Black people are on welfare, 
but so are alot of whites. Sure, alot of Black people commit crimes, 
but what do you call people like DAHMER, FURHMAN, or PACKWOOD for that 
matter? Saints!  STATISTICS generalize and so do idiots!

<p>In conclusion, Mr. Truth stated that Blacks are dead weight over the 
shoulders of each REGULAR-American. I would like to know from Mr.Truth 
what the hell is a REGULAR-American? IF your answer is white then 
