<p><tt>Sat Jul 22 19:54 EDT 1995</tt>

<p>Dear Sirs,

I enjoy your web page very much, but I don't believe you go far
enough in content.  Please let me explain.  If the average white 
person is ever going to truly understand the reality of the 
differences which exist between the white race and the black race,
they MUST be allowed to view the statistical data which so plainly
and clearly illustates all the points you and I are trying to make.
The liberal media "shields" the average person from the true facts,
because to do otherwise would be "insensitive" or not "politically
correct."  

<P>The true numbers are staggering!  Blacks are ravaging the
nation with crime, and the liberal media is worried about offending
certain members of society with the truth!!!  A sign of the times, 
my friends.  If you'll observe, the media seemingly always points to
crime statistices, HIV/AIDS statistics, illegitimate birth rate
statistics, and health statistics in terms of ALL races combined.  
However, when you actually take the time to read the race dependent
numbers (e.g. The stats which catagorize sets of data according to
race) published by such government organizations as, The Centers For
Disease Control,  The Federal Bureau of Investigation, and the Central
Intelligence Agency, it rapidly becomes apparent that the black
community is responsible for a very large and disproportionate amount
of crime and HIV/AIDS in this country!  The media also fails to
indicate that if you are white, and you practice heterosexual sex
with a partner of your own race and whose practices are the same as 
yours, your chances of contracting HIV are far, far lower than those
of homosexuals, blacks, and illicit drug users.  How is it that blacks
comprise less than 13 percent of our society, and account for so much
turmoil?  Read "The Bell Curve" for a better understanding!  Sirs, I
strongly encourage you to produce numerous graphs on your WWW page
which clearly illustrate what the liberal media tries so hard to hide.
If you can help to force these numbers into the light, more people
might join our common cause.  Sadly, because of the media, many people
just aren't aware of the truth.  And if you do decide to create 
graphs, be sure to include the U.S. Goverment sources from which the 
data originates.  This will lend additional credibility to the data.
Otherwise, the liberal media will simply discount the data as being
misrepresented by "right-wing extremists"!  Finally, let me encourage
each of you to vote Republican during the next election!

<P>Sirs, feel free to print this letter, but please withhold my email
address.  I work for the U.S. Government and my job would be at 
jeopardy if it is discovered that I'm writing letters like this one
while I'm at work.  (I know, it's very sad that the "PC" crowd is
killing the first amendment.)  I am very proud of my political
position, but I can't afford to lose my job.  I don't hate all blacks,
and I don't love all whites.  I just feel the country would be
better off without them (blacks) as a whole, and they'd be better off 
back in their natural habitat.  If they continue to stay, they will 
continue to be like a huge "dead weight" over the shoulders of each
REGULAR-American.
   
