<h3><i>What kind of people do YOU want living in your Utopia?</i></h3>

<p>This is more or less a follow on from my previous posting on the eight
year old asian girl who had ciggarettes stubbed out on her back by a
racist white guy. One person who claimed to be a member of the Ku Klux 
Klan said he would have gone further and tied the girl to a cartwheel 
and shoved barbed wire into her bodily orifices.

<p>What I want to ask is whether white separatists want people like this 
living in your white Utopia?  Do you realy want someone who do something
like that to a little girl (whatever her colour).  Do you want someone
who'd sooner stub out cigarrettes on a little girl's back than give you
the time of the day.  After all, to do something like that takes more
than 'having pride in your race'.  It takes a person who has something
wrong in their head.

<p>Let's take this further.  Say you where in a balloon 25000 feet above
the Atlantic with an asian doctor (who'd treat anyone regardless of 
skin colour) and a  racist white guy who couldn't find his butt if you
gave him a map. You need to throw someone out because you're running 
out of hot air.  Who would you throw out?

