<BODY>
<img align=left src="images/z_fire.jpg" alt="Z&uuml;ndel's Burned Out Home" hspace=15 vspace=5><h1>Z&uuml;ndel House Burned</h1>
 
<p>At approximately 5:30 a.m. on Sunday, May 7, the Toronto home and headquarters of Ernst Z&uuml;ndel, the German-Canadian revisionist publisher, was attacked by arsonist(s).
 
<p>The large Victorian home suffered extensive damage to the upper story. It was occupied at the time of the attack, though not by Mr. Z&uuml;ndel who was in western Canada.
 
<p>A surveillance camera captured the perpetator(s) dousing the front of the building with an inflammatory substance, presumably gasoline. A videotape of the attack has been turned over to Toronto police.
 
<p>The building was insured but not the contents. Some of Mr. Z&uuml;ndel's priceless files pertaining to his two historic trials for publishing the book <b><i>Did Six
Million Really Die?</i></b> were lost in the fire.

<img align=right src="images/Zundel.jpg" alt="Ernst Z&uuml;ndel" hspace=15 vspace=5> 

<p>Arson of an occupied building constitutes attempted murder.
 
<p>The Z&uuml;ndel house, located in a bohemian neighborhood, has for years been the
target of leftist groups. Recently their threats escalated.
 
<p>For further information telephone 416-922-9850.
 
<p>Contributions may be sent to Ernst Z&uuml;ndel, Samisdat Publishing Co., 206 Carlton Street, Toronto, M5A 2L1 Canada.

<p><i>ANA -- Kleim</i>

<hr size=4 noshade>

<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=582 HEIGHT=19 BORDER=0 ALIGN=TOP SRC="images/bomb1.gif"></CENTER>

<center><h3>Terrorist Alert  --  Terrorist Alert  --  Terrorist Alert</h3></center>

<center><h2>$5000 Reward</h2></center>
<p>

<p><b>For information leading to the arrest and conviction of the arsonist and conspirators responsible for the terrorist attack on Ernst Z&uuml;ndel's 206 Carlton Street office and home on Sunday, May 7, 1995, approximately 5:30 a.m.</b>
<hr>

<p><b><i>Fact:</i></b> A New York-based group, claiming to be an offshoot of the Jewish Defence League (JDL) claimed responsibility for the firebombing.

<p><b><i>Fact:</i></b> In 1985 the Jewish Defence League was declared a major terrorist group by the FBI.

<p><b><i>Fact:</i></b> On Friday, May 12 at 4:30 p.m., just five days after the arson attack, the U.S. National Director of the JDL, <b>Irv Rubin</b>, along with longtime Canadian JDL leader, <b>Meir Haley</b>, and members of the radical ARA attempted
to breach a protective barrier at the Z&uuml;ndel location.

<p><b><i>Fact:</i></b> The culprits were questioned by police and released, but media outlets chose <b><i>not</i></b> to inform the public of this specter  of international terrorism.

<p><b><i>Fact:</i></b> By 1979, the LA-based Rubin had been arrested on 39 JDL-related activities.  In March '92, he was arrested on suspicion of  conspiring to commit murder.

<p><b><i>Question:</i></b> Why was Irv Rubin, a man with an extensive record of violence, <b><i>allowed</i></b> to enter Canada?

<p><b><i>Question:</i></b> Do Canadian politicians and media outlets <b><i>approve</i></b> of international
terrorism as long as it is of the "politically correct" variety?

<p><b><i>Question:</i></b> Is this the future of Canadian politics?

<hr>

<center><h4>If you have any information regarding this matter,</h4></center>
<center><h4>call Ernst Z&uuml;ndel at (416) 922-9859 or the Metropolitan Toronto Police.</h4></center>
       
<p><i>(Transcribers note:  This flyer is in front of Mr. Z&uuml;ndel's house pasted to the protective barrier and is being passed around to local citizens in the Toronto area.  There also was a segment of a show called "Crime Stoppers" which aired the unclear pictures of the person from Z&uuml;ndel's cameras above his house).</i>

