<title>Up Front 18--Feedback: The Letter File </title>
</head>
<BODY background="images/upfront!bkg.gif">

<IMG WIDTH=72 HEIGHT=77 HSPACE=15 BORDER=0 ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="images/upfront!s.gif">
<center><IMG WIDTH=470 HEIGHT=6 BORDER=0 ALIGN=TOP SRC="images/gradlin2.gif"></center>
<h1>Feedback--The Letter File</h1>

<h3>Our readers write - and we reply</h3>

<p><i>In keeping with Up Front's policy of respecting anonymity, most
writers will be identified solely by the first three characters of
their postal or zip codes.</i>

<p><i>Opinions expressed herein are those of the writers, and do not
necessarily reflect those of </i><strong>The Heritage Front, Up Front,</strong><i> or its
staff. Letters may be edited for brevity.</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear <strong>Up Front</strong>:
<p>While I thoroughly enjoyed your lengthy article on the traitorous
spy Grant Bristow, I have a problem with the way you chose to
criticize and mock <i>Toronto Sun</i> reporter, Bill Dunphy.
<p>Your article claims that many people were suspicious of the mole
from the beginning:
<p>- 1. an NPC drunk stated, "looks like a cop to me"
<p>- 2. Droege and Lincoln chose to brush off these accusations, even
though they too, had strong suspicions.
<p>- 3. Gary Schipper crowed, "we knew he was a rat."
<p>Yet, none of you did anything to correct the problem. It took Bill
Dunphy to expose the rat Bristow. And even after the rest of the
media ran with the story, it was Dunphy who analyzed the situation
and put things in their proper perspective.
<p>In my humble opinion, Mr. Dunphy is a brilliant investigative
journalist with an uncanny talent for observation. It seems we all
owe him a debt of gratitude.
<p>I wish to remain anonymous at this time.
<p>M5A
<p><i>Is that you Bill?</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear Heritage Front:
<p>After reading "Adios El Observador" on the Internet, I was
intrigued. I wish to order a copy of the "Bristow" issue of your
magazine. Enclosed please find $30.00.
<p>920
<p><i>For $30.00 we'll throw in the video too.</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear <strong>Up Front</strong> readers:
<p>Although our ruling elite are doing their best to prevent us from
looking at crime statistics based on race, it is common knowledge
who is committing the majority of crimes in our multiracial
paradise.
<p>Even though they are still a minority, even in Toronto, more than
three-quarters of all violent and drug-related crimes are
perpetrated by one group. A holdup squad officer, who did not want
to be named mentioned a figure of 85%.
<p>Even with our toothless justice system which regularly releases
them back into the community revolving door-style, this group now
comprises a large segment of our prison population.
<p>Our rulers, the liberal media and other ethnic screamers have
deigned to spare us these stats, but if the race of an assailant is
not reported, you can safely assume that he is not White.
<p>The absurdity of crime reporting becomes ridiculous when one hears
a criminal's description broadcast on the radio: The suspect is
five-feet-ten, a hundred and sixty pounds, with short hair, wearing
a blue jacket and a red baseball cap.
<p>TV journalists use their own bag of tricks. Recently they showed
footage of a suspect, arrested for a convenience store holdup. The
camera operator was careful to shoot well below the knees of the
suspect - not even the palms of his hands were showing. But his
day-glo green track pants told me all I needed to know.
<p>Is our media really all that different from the old PRAVDA of the
Soviet Union?
<p>M6G
<p><i>We learn to read between the lines.</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear Heritage Front:
<p>With a fine organization like the HF why do some of these little
Mickey Mouse organizations insist on trying to compete with you
rather than working alongside to further our cause?
<p>M8Z
<p><i>According to Milton, 'tis better to rule in hell than serve in
heaven.</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear Canadian Nationalists:
<p>Very little is known about Canada in Sweden (except when it
concerns hockey) and even less about your racial situation. After
having read the South African magazine <i>Impact</i> I have come to
realize that Canada has just as great - perhaps even greater -
problems with multiracialism and liberalism as Sweden, Europe and
the rest of the White world.
<p>Canada and Sweden are in many ways similar. Both sparsely
populated, with non-germanic minorities, and breathtaking scenery
throughout our land. We are both bilingual, Canada, English and
French, Sweden, Swedish and Finnish. I don't know about
Canada, but in Sweden the fastest growing religion today is -
Islam!
<p>I simply cannot believe that so many people have bought the
liberal-communist lies about the equality of all races.
<p>I have often wondered why - in the liberal mind - only the Left
can be oppressed; never the Right or Nationalists. In Germany you
can get five years in prison for denying the Holocaust. How many
years do you get for denying Stalin's murders? Have you ever heard
Amnesty International protest?
<p>I take great interest in the racial situation all over the White
world. I would therefore like to obtain a copy of your publication,
<strong>Up Front</strong>, and for that I enclose SEK 40 (CDN $7.40).
<p>Swedish Reader
<p><i>We keep hearing horror stories about the train station in
Stockholm.</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear <strong>Up Front</strong>:
<p>Thank you for the November issue of <strong>Up Front</strong>. My son (23) raved
about it. Your magazine has good substance (subjects, facts and
presentation) that will appeal even to middle-aged and "timid"
Canadians. I sincerely hope that you will always strive to maintain
and even improve upon your public image.
<p>M2J
<p><i>You can help - share this magazine with your like-minded friends.</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear Heritage Front:
<p>It amazes me how much abuse at the hands of the leftists we take.
<p>The majority of our people sit on their butts, drink beer and watch
hockey while their brains run in reverse.
<p>In the <i>Etobicoke Guardian</i>, a community newspaper, dated January
11, 1995, the headline ran "SOMALI GROUP RECEIVES GRANT." In 1993
several groups within the Somali community formed a coalition to
aid new immigrants from the death-ravaged cesspool that they call
their homeland.
<p>As the story goes, this coalition received $75,000 from the
Ontario Ministry of Citizenship and Immigration Canada, the
Department of Canadian Heritage and the municipality of Metro
Toronto, with in-kind assistance from the United Way.
<p>This grant will help the tribesmen adjust to their new life as
"Canadians" (yeah, right!). The Family Services Association of
Metro Toronto will assist the "coalition" with the project startup
and operational phase, then turn all operations over to the
coalition.
<p>The project will be titled "DIJINTA BEESHA." (What a handle!)
<p>This is a blatant example of government waste. They don't dare to
go to the people to ask if this is an acceptable use of their tax
dollars, because they know bloody well that if asked, the majority
would respond with a resounding "NO!"
<p>Instead, they quietly implement any left-wing commie plan that
they see fit to, and we foot the bill.
<p>M9V
<p><i>Our government grant - Grant Bristow - produced more positive
results than can ever be expected from "Dejinta Deesha."</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear <strong>Up Front</strong>:
<p>The recent Republican win in the U.S. shows that Americans are fed
up with liberal nonsense. The `Silent Majority' has spoken, but
will the G.O.P. hear them, or will they cave to special interest
pressure?
<p>701
<p><i>Media control is a must if we are to prevail. The Internet is a
first step.</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear <strong>Up Front</strong>:
<p>The PC line is that "immigrants enrich Canada." Right now, how
many Third Worlders have just thought to themselves: "I must go to
Canada and enrich those poor souls." Better for us they should take
their benevolence and "enrich" their brothers in Uganda or Somalia.
<p>V9S
<p><i>And put all those creepy immigration lawyers out of work?</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear Heritage Front:
<p>While perusing a bulletin board at the Mississauga Central
Library, I spotted an advertisement for free ESL (English Second
Language) courses sponsored by some organization.
<p>Now we all know that nothing is really free. Who pays? You and I!
<p>Who can't speak English? Surely not you or me - we were born here!
<p>Who benefits? Three guesses! Who paid all the taxes to build the
schools and the teachers' salaries? You and I did!
<p>And who will leave when the economy collapses and there are no
jobs and the welfare runs dry? I don't have to spell it out, do I?
<p>And who will be left to clean up the mess? You and I, of course.
<p>Who should stop this mess before it really hits the fan? You and
I!
<p>L5C
<p><i>It should have been nipped in the bud. The longer we wait, the
harder it will be.</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear <strong>Up Front</strong>:
<p>I've never bothered to formulate an opinion on abortion, one way
or the other, so this is just an observation.
<p>I find it ironic that on the one hand the government takes a "pro-
choice" stance and legalizes and sanctions the killing of an unborn
fetus, yet on the other, they ignore the convictions of a religious
sect, forcing parents to submit their children to blood
transfusions against their will. Is this not a double standard?
<p>L9A
<p><i>Politicians are consistent only in the application of double
standards.</i>
<hr>
<p>Dear <strong>Up Front</strong>:
<p>I was impressed by Wolfgang Droege's remarkable showing at the
polls during the recent municipal elections.
<p>Fourteen percent of the vote is quite an achievement, when one considers the
handicap he endured. And I believe that 14% is the largest vote
garnered by any openly racialist candidate to run in Canada since
the Second World War. In a system of proportional representation,
this could have translated to a seat on city council.
<p>Despite a court-imposed gag order which forbade him from talking
to the media, he made sure that everyone in his ward received his
election pamphlet. So, I believe that he received a vote which is
fairly reflective of the population at large. I'm sure no one was
misled or ignorant as to who they were voting for. Although they're
slow to admit it, many people are starting to realize that race is
one of the most important issues facing us today. Ironically,
negative media coverage made sure of that.
<p>It's comforting to know that at least 14% of the population is
with us, sharing our views and ideas.
<p>I would also like to congratulate all the other Heritage Front
candidates for their courage in standing up for their (and our)
beliefs, and putting their names on the ballot. Their bravery in
challenging the political elite on important and taboo subjects
like race deserves our thanks.
<p>In particular, Lorna Houston displayed immense courage. Having
endured harassment, threats and disruptions by rabid leftists at
an all-candidates meeting, she stood her ground, never faltering in
the promotion of views generally regarded as unacceptable by
today's mind controllers. She is to be commended.
<p>Enclosed is $50 to help the HF carry on its important work. It's
not much compared to the huge amounts spent by our political
opponents who receive their funding from wealthy corporate donors,
and even the government. But being a working man, it's all my
budget will allow.
<p>M1E
<p><i>The ineptness of our current leaders assures the growth of the HF</i>
<P>

